race.comment: STORMS WILL ROLL (3) has hit the frame here at the last two runs, most recently finishing second beaten a neck (19.65). Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to his credit. Deserves a win and gets his chance. BEELINE (2) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with two wins and a placing from four tries. Comes off a (19.77) win last time, scoring by 1.75 lengths in a Mix 6/7 over 350m at this track. Makes strong appeal on best. SODA TURKEY (6) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at this track over 350m (19.93). A big run wouldn't surprise. EAGLE TROOPER (1) can measure up with the right run.
